text: Hello! Im about to finish my Certification Practicum for developers II and im having an issue with autogenerated id's that replicate. Im having that problem to pass the axeDevtools scan but i can't control those ids from being autogenerated. Any thoughts on how to fix this problem? Thanks! <@UQNEXHW14>
Hello Juan, unfortunately, I am not sure of a fix for this, but because this is HubSpot-generated, we don't mark you off for this!
Ok perfect! So i'm ready to submit the link then!! Thanks for you answer!
